 &lt;p&gt;The Hexo Advanced Image Optimizer Plugin enhances your Hexo site by leveraging the power of &lt;code&gt;wsrv.nl&lt;/code&gt;, a high-performance image cache and resize service. Powered by Cloudflareâ€™s CDN, it delivers images from over 300 global datacenters, ensuring lightning-fast load times and optimal performance. With support for advanced image processing using technologies like nginx and libvips, this plugin transforms and optimizes images on-the-fly. Itâ€™s open-source, free to use, and seamlessly integrates with Hexo to process markdown images, cover images, CSS background images, and &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;object&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; tags.&lt;/p&gt;
